text: Eugène Mougin was an archer from France. He was born on 17 November 1852 and died on 28 December 1924. Mougin competed at the 1900 Summer Olympics.Eugène MouginEugène MOUGIN == References == Category:1852 births Category:1924 deaths Category:French archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for France
